data.description: This pristine 2-story craftsman home in close-in Dallas offers a low-maintenance lifestyle that's hard to beat. With a compact, hassle-free backyard oasis, you can enjoy the outdoors without the work. The icing on the cake is its proximity to the Heritage Club's neighborhood amenities, which feature a beautiful pool, tennis courts and a playground. Inside, the home boasts spacious living areas and 4 bedrooms, with 2-1/2 half baths. The open-concept family room with fireplace seamlessly connects to the kitchen, making it the heart of the home. A dramatic two-story foyer welcomes you in, while an additional formal living room offers versatile space for an office, study, or music room. The separate dining room has an elegance with its upgraded trim, and a half-bath on the main floor adds to your convenience. Upstairs, you'll find your personal sanctuary in the oversized master bedroom, complete with a private ensuite bathroom that includes a double vanity, separate shower, soaking tub, separate toilet, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms upstairs share a spacious bathroom, and a separate laundry room with a linen closet offers everyday convenience. Located close-in to Dallas Hwy, Thornton Rd, the Silver Comet Trail, and the Historical City of Dallas, this beautiful, well-maintained home is ready for you to make it your own. Envision yourself here – it's a move-in-ready dream!
